[*] Test: bare refs inside loops and parallel blocks

/Fetch [U]: a url
	[>] data from [U]

/Transform [D]: data
	[>] cleaned [D]

/Pipeline
[V]: a list of urls
	[~] — [U] in [V]
		[1] — [D]: Fetch[ [U] ]
		[^] WARNING: bare ref to Fetch
		[2] — [R]: /Transform[ [D] ]
		[^] OK: proper ref

	[&]
		[1] — [A]: Fetch[ url1 ]
		[^] WARNING: bare ref to Fetch
		[2] — [B]: Fetch[ url2 ]
		[^] WARNING: bare ref to Fetch
	[3] — /Transform[ [A] ]
	[^] OK: proper ref
